          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2018-06-04T20:59:42Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Pay for Printing Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the sponsor of a ceremonial or commemorative Senate resolution to reimburse the Government Publishing Office for the total costs of printing the resolution out of the sponsor's Senators' Official Personnel and Office Expense Account.</p> <p>It excludes from such requirement a resolution sponsored by at least two-thirds of the Senators.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-05-22T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
        </item>
